sentences.english: NO02,3. Let me show you where the printer is.
sentences.chinese: 我來告訴你印表機在哪裏。
無法重新啓動印表機伺服器。

sentences.english: High quality inkjet printer can produce adequate image for A. P. P.
sentences.chinese: 高階的印表機可以製造出可接受的日光顯影影像。

sentences.english: You may use an online printer to print out the data.
sentences.chinese: 你可以使用連線印表機把資料列印出來。

sentences.english: Test page successfully sent to printer.
sentences.chinese: 測試頁已經成功的送至印表機。

sentences.english: Pages of the report spewed out from the computer printer.
sentences.chinese: 一頁又一頁的報告從印表機輸出。

sentences.english: But two users cannot use the printer at the same time.
sentences.chinese: 但有兩個用戶無法使用同一臺印表機的時間。
您以前有使用過印表機嗎？

sentences.english: You must select at least one printer.
sentences.chinese: 您必須選擇至少一個印表機。

sentences.english: The printer is the most commonly used output device after the monitor.
sentences.chinese: 印表機是除顯示器外最常用的輸出設備。

sentences.english: Dot-matrix printer, free for faculty, staff and students of NCU.
sentences.chinese: 點矩陣印表機，可免費使用。

sentences.english: The printer has a one-year warranty, so I have the right to do so.
sentences.chinese: 這臺印表機有一年的保固期，所以我有權這麼做。

sentences.english: I forgot to connect my printer to my computer.
sentences.chinese: 我忘記將我的印表機與我的電腦連線。
